WEBVTT

01:43.440 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:15.040 --> 02:17.880
<i>There are several unforgettable moments
throughout our lives.</i>

02:19.680 --> 02:20.520
<i>No.</i>

02:21.480 --> 02:22.840
<i>To be more precise,</i>

02:23.400 --> 02:25.480
<i>several paused temporal nodes.</i>

02:26.160 --> 02:28.160
ISAAC ASIMOV: THE END OF ETERNITY

02:28.240 --> 02:29.680
DUAN

02:29.760 --> 02:31.120
Busted, thief.

02:42.880 --> 02:44.360
<i>This is my second time</i>

02:45.080 --> 02:46.720
<i>looking at him so closely.</i>

02:50.320 --> 02:52.720
<i>Time does have magic</i>

02:53.760 --> 02:54.960
<i>drawing us closer in height</i>

02:55.600 --> 02:56.600
<i>and distance.</i>

02:59.720 --> 03:00.960
In the Pythagorean theorem,

03:01.040 --> 03:03.720
A squared plus B squared

03:03.800 --> 03:07.920
equals the square of C, the longest side.

03:09.680 --> 03:10.520
Sang Zhi.

03:12.480 --> 03:13.360
Sang Zhi!

03:14.080 --> 03:15.160
What are you staring at?

03:17.200 --> 03:18.600
Just now, a mother bird

03:18.680 --> 03:20.480
brought back food to feed baby birds.

03:20.560 --> 03:22.160
The two baby birds were fighting for it.

03:22.240 --> 03:24.160
Then the mother bird flew away

03:24.240 --> 03:25.560
with the food.

03:25.640 --> 03:27.600
They were then stunned

03:27.680 --> 03:29.480
for one or two minutes.

03:29.560 --> 03:30.560
They were frozen.

03:32.240 --> 03:33.480
Be quiet, everyone.

03:33.560 --> 03:34.840
Sang Zhi.

03:34.920 --> 03:36.720
Pay attention

03:36.800 --> 03:37.920
and look at the board.

03:39.560 --> 03:40.880
Sit down.

03:40.960 --> 03:43.000
Let's read the third question aloud.

03:43.560 --> 03:46.720
- "A triangle ABC
- "A triangle ABC

03:46.800 --> 03:47.720
- with side lengths
- with side lengths

03:47.800 --> 03:50.600
- of 5 cm, 13 cm, and 12 cm."
- of 5 cm, 13 cm, and 12 cm."

03:50.680 --> 03:51.680
Obviously,

03:52.360 --> 03:55.200
we can see that the longest length

03:55.280 --> 03:56.520
is C.

03:57.560 --> 03:59.080
So

03:59.160 --> 04:00.400
how do we get this?

04:01.560 --> 04:03.480
Equals 5…

04:04.120 --> 04:06.840
The conditions given

04:08.520 --> 04:11.440
are that the side lengths are A and B.

04:11.520 --> 04:13.760
What kind of triangle is this?

04:13.840 --> 04:17.240
- "A right triangle."
- "A right triangle."

04:17.320 --> 04:18.839
Multiply the base by the height
and divide by two.

04:18.920 --> 04:19.880
Look at this.

04:19.959 --> 04:21.880
You've picked this up, right?

04:21.959 --> 04:22.960
Next question.

04:23.040 --> 04:26.560
Angle one equals angle two.

04:28.960 --> 04:31.360
Angle three is 108 degrees.

04:34.920 --> 04:35.760
Sang Zhi!

04:37.800 --> 04:38.640
Sang Zhi.

04:46.280 --> 04:48.000
Where was I just now?

04:54.840 --> 04:56.040
Angle four equals 72 degrees.

05:01.240 --> 05:02.720
I haven't gotten there yet.

05:05.160 --> 05:06.880
Where were you just now?

05:07.840 --> 05:09.000
Silence.

05:09.080 --> 05:10.080
Silence!

05:10.560 --> 05:12.400
Angle one equals angle two,

05:12.480 --> 05:14.640
so line AB is parallel to line CD.

05:14.720 --> 05:15.960
As they are parallel lines,

05:16.040 --> 05:17.720
same-side interior angles
are supplementary.

05:17.800 --> 05:19.600
- So angle three is--
- Stop.

05:20.160 --> 05:21.400
It's not about the question.

05:22.040 --> 05:23.600
It's your attitude!

05:24.160 --> 05:25.920
Sang Zhi, tomorrow,

05:27.160 --> 05:28.560
have your parents come in.

05:30.880 --> 05:31.720
Sit down.

05:35.520 --> 05:36.480
Let's continue.

05:37.560 --> 05:39.120
Angle one equals angle two.

05:39.880 --> 05:41.920
This means that these two straight lines

05:42.000 --> 05:43.920
are parallel to each other.

05:44.800 --> 05:46.360
The interior angles are supplementary.

05:47.120 --> 05:49.680
Therefore, calculate angle four.

05:50.400 --> 05:52.480
GRADE 8, CLASS 1

05:52.560 --> 05:54.240
- Let's go home.
- Go!

05:54.840 --> 05:55.960
I'm sorry about earlier.

05:56.040 --> 05:57.240
I pointed to the wrong line

05:58.160 --> 06:00.080
and the teacher caught you again.

06:00.160 --> 06:01.480
Your mom has already come in twice

06:01.560 --> 06:02.960
in just half a month.

06:03.800 --> 06:05.400
I don't know
if I rubbed him the wrong way.

06:06.040 --> 06:06.960
But when you replied

06:07.040 --> 06:09.080
with his own question,

06:09.160 --> 06:10.160
I felt like punching you,

06:10.240 --> 06:11.520
let alone Mr. Chen.

06:12.680 --> 06:15.040
Don't you think his voice is hypnotizing?

06:15.120 --> 06:16.520
I would've dozed off

06:16.600 --> 06:17.840
if I didn't do something.

06:17.920 --> 06:18.920
You're right.

06:20.800 --> 06:22.400
But why do you always get caught by him?

06:23.720 --> 06:24.720
It never happened to me.

06:27.840 --> 06:30.840
Ask her if she wants
to go to the bookstore.

06:32.960 --> 06:33.840
Let's go.

06:37.560 --> 06:39.160
Do you want to go to the bookstore?

06:40.160 --> 06:41.040
Why?

06:41.920 --> 06:43.200
Fu Zhengchu invited us

06:43.280 --> 06:45.480
and also some boys from his class.

06:46.120 --> 06:47.040
Let's go together.

06:47.560 --> 06:48.520
Why do you want to go?

06:49.320 --> 06:51.520
To buy study materials.

06:52.120 --> 06:53.560
Are you coming along?

06:53.640 --> 06:54.520
No.

06:57.040 --> 06:59.720
Coming?

07:01.520 --> 07:03.480
<i>Sang Yan, you've been away for a while.</i>

07:03.560 --> 07:04.560
<i>When are you coming home?</i>

07:05.280 --> 07:06.840
<i>Can you come back tomorrow?</i>

07:07.600 --> 07:09.160
<i>I miss you so much.</i>

07:09.240 --> 07:10.480
So are you coming?

07:10.560 --> 07:11.960
No, I'm not going.

07:12.040 --> 07:14.200
But they're waiting over there.

07:14.280 --> 07:15.160
Let's go, please.

07:16.040 --> 07:17.640
Go ahead if you want.

07:17.720 --> 07:18.760
I'm not in the mood today.

07:18.840 --> 07:20.520
Is it because your parents have to come?

07:21.720 --> 07:22.880
What do you plan to do?

07:23.840 --> 07:25.360
They're not coming.

07:25.440 --> 07:26.960
Even so,

07:27.040 --> 07:29.200
Mr. Chen will call them.

07:29.280 --> 07:32.080
That's why I asked my brother to come.

07:32.960 --> 07:33.840
He replied.

07:37.720 --> 07:38.560
I'm leaving.

07:41.200 --> 07:42.080
- Wait.
- Sang Zhi.

07:42.720 --> 07:43.920
Bye.

07:44.000 --> 07:45.280
Sang Zhi, why are you leaving?

07:45.360 --> 07:46.760
Aren't you coming to the bookstore?

07:47.240 --> 07:48.480
Is Sang Zhi not coming?

07:48.560 --> 07:49.960
The teacher scolded her.

07:50.040 --> 07:51.200
She's feeling down.

07:51.280 --> 07:52.440
Are her parents coming again?

07:54.160 --> 07:56.640
Her parents come more often
than yours, Fu Zhengchu.

07:56.720 --> 07:57.720
Shame on you.

07:59.000 --> 08:00.360
Mind your own business.

08:02.720 --> 08:04.480
Why won't he help me?

08:19.920 --> 08:22.040
<i>Sang Yan, you're heartless.</i>

08:23.800 --> 08:24.640
<i>Sure.</i>

08:24.720 --> 08:25.560
SILLY DOG

08:25.640 --> 08:27.560
<i>You abandoned me
after going to university!</i>

08:28.520 --> 08:29.560
<i>Sure.</i>

08:31.720 --> 08:33.360
<i>You're leaving me to struggle by myself!</i>

08:34.320 --> 08:35.520
<i>Sure.</i>

08:37.080 --> 08:38.960
ANGRY, GOING TO BE ANGRY, ANNOYED

08:47.360 --> 08:49.720
How am I going to face Dad and Mom?

08:51.000 --> 08:52.760
I won't let it go that easily, Silly Dog.

08:59.640 --> 09:00.960
What should I do?

09:03.760 --> 09:04.600
Doggy.

09:06.720 --> 09:07.600
Come here.

09:08.840 --> 09:10.600
You're so adorable.

09:12.600 --> 09:14.520
Do you know? Sang Yan, that silly dog,

09:14.600 --> 09:16.640
left me on my own and even angered me.

09:16.720 --> 09:18.200
You think he's hateful, right?

09:18.280 --> 09:20.880
Listen, you mustn't grow into
a big silly dog like him

09:20.960 --> 09:22.200
in the future.

09:22.280 --> 09:23.640
Though you're a small silly dog,

09:23.720 --> 09:25.440
don't grow up to be like him, okay?

09:29.600 --> 09:30.880
You're good in this way.

09:33.200 --> 09:34.760
Are you going to make me angry too?

09:34.840 --> 09:36.080
Is that how it is?

09:36.160 --> 09:37.680
I'm sure you'll become a big silly dog,

09:38.720 --> 09:39.840
just like Sang Yan.

10:05.080 --> 10:06.000
Zhizhi, welcome home.

10:17.840 --> 10:18.720
Mom.

10:19.360 --> 10:20.520
Listen.

10:20.600 --> 10:21.480
- The--
- Hold on.

10:25.000 --> 10:26.840
Take the fruit upstairs.

10:27.840 --> 10:28.760
Sang Yan is back.

10:29.720 --> 10:30.680
He's back?

10:31.200 --> 10:32.040
Yes.

10:32.120 --> 10:33.560
Be careful when you go upstairs.

10:33.640 --> 10:34.720
- Okay.
- He--

10:38.360 --> 10:39.720
She's rather weird today.

10:49.320 --> 10:50.160
Sang Yan!

11:05.560 --> 11:06.480
What's up?

11:08.960 --> 11:10.640
Did you get plastic surgery?

11:14.480 --> 11:15.760
Come over and see

11:15.840 --> 11:17.240
if the results are good.

11:26.960 --> 11:27.840
What's wrong with you?

11:28.360 --> 11:29.600
Are you amazed by my dashing look?

11:30.880 --> 11:33.080
You're more narcissistic than me,
Sang Yan.

11:33.920 --> 11:35.080
Shut up.

11:36.320 --> 11:37.480
Little demon, tell me now.

11:37.560 --> 11:38.680
What have you done this time?

11:39.520 --> 11:40.720
No, I did nothing.

11:41.600 --> 11:42.480
No?

11:43.040 --> 11:44.160
How is that possible?

11:44.240 --> 11:46.280
Why else would you say you miss me

11:46.360 --> 11:47.480
and ask me to come home?

11:51.840 --> 11:53.560
Sang Yan, something did come up.

11:53.640 --> 11:54.760
Is she your sister, Sang Yan?

11:55.960 --> 11:57.200
Do you think she's my daughter?

12:02.160 --> 12:03.000
Sang Yan.

12:03.520 --> 12:04.560
Who is he?

12:05.960 --> 12:07.280
My roommate, Duan Jiaxu.

12:15.040 --> 12:16.160
Hello, little girl.

12:16.240 --> 12:17.720
I'm Duan Jiaxu.

12:17.800 --> 12:19.040
I'm your brother's friend.

12:22.760 --> 12:24.800
Do we look alike?

12:27.520 --> 12:28.560
The bathroom is over there.

12:28.640 --> 12:29.960
Take a look in the mirror.

12:30.040 --> 12:31.120
Who looks like you?

12:32.160 --> 12:33.120
Really?

12:33.200 --> 12:35.040
But your sister just asked me

12:35.120 --> 12:36.720
if I got plastic surgery.

12:41.960 --> 12:42.800
What do you mean?

12:44.800 --> 12:46.040
Sang Yan, didn't you say

12:46.120 --> 12:47.920
you weren't coming back today?

12:52.640 --> 12:55.160
Little demon,
don't tell me you mistook him for me

12:55.240 --> 12:56.760
and a tweaked version of me at that!

12:58.640 --> 12:59.520
Little demon,

12:59.600 --> 13:00.960
what do you think about every day?

13:01.040 --> 13:02.240
What is on your mind?

13:02.320 --> 13:03.200
You…

13:03.280 --> 13:04.480
Stop!

13:05.440 --> 13:07.320
Isn't plastic surgery
the obvious conclusion?

13:07.400 --> 13:08.720
Look at your ugly face.

13:08.800 --> 13:10.320
Besides, Mom didn't tell me

13:10.400 --> 13:11.320
you brought a friend.

13:11.400 --> 13:13.720
Moreover, he was the only one in the room.

13:13.800 --> 13:15.400
Naturally, I mistook him for you!

13:18.160 --> 13:19.000
Keep it down!

13:19.080 --> 13:20.200
Why should I?

13:20.280 --> 13:21.120
You're too loud!

13:22.760 --> 13:23.880
You can't beat me.

13:23.960 --> 13:24.800
Here, little girl.

13:26.960 --> 13:28.400
Have some fruit.

13:29.240 --> 13:30.320
Don't bother with him.

13:32.680 --> 13:33.720
Duan Jiaxu,

13:33.800 --> 13:35.280
do you want to shower before leaving?

13:35.360 --> 13:37.560
No. Go get changed so we can go.

13:37.640 --> 13:39.080
All right. I'm going to get changed.

13:39.920 --> 13:41.280
- Hurry up.
- Wait!

13:41.360 --> 13:43.320
Sang Yan, I need your help.

13:43.400 --> 13:44.280
Move.

13:44.360 --> 13:45.800
I'm in a rush to get plastic surgery.

13:45.880 --> 13:48.040
I'm sorry.

13:48.120 --> 13:49.040
Too bad.

13:49.920 --> 13:51.320
Are you leaving me for dead?

13:51.400 --> 13:53.400
I don't even know what you're asking for.

13:53.880 --> 13:55.120
Shoot. What is it?

13:56.120 --> 13:57.960
Please say yes first.

13:59.400 --> 14:00.280
I can't do that.

14:03.800 --> 14:05.320
Are you going to report me to Mom?

14:11.440 --> 14:12.320
Mom!

14:12.880 --> 14:13.760
Mom!

14:14.640 --> 14:15.680
Mom!

14:17.520 --> 14:18.920
Mom!

14:20.880 --> 14:22.640
You were laughing just now. What happened?

14:22.720 --> 14:25.720
Mom, Sang Yan beat me!

14:25.800 --> 14:26.640
Mom!

14:29.680 --> 14:32.320
- Mom, Sang Yan beat me!
- Sang Yan.

14:32.400 --> 14:34.120
Can you not do that to your sister?

14:36.160 --> 14:37.520
Mom!

14:44.960 --> 14:45.880
Stop that.

14:46.480 --> 14:48.200
Why shush her? How dare you bully her!

14:48.760 --> 14:50.920
Mom, Sang Yan beat me.

14:51.000 --> 14:52.680
- He said I…
- All right, dear.

14:52.760 --> 14:53.800
Don't cry.

14:53.880 --> 14:54.920
How could you?

14:55.000 --> 14:56.160
I'll teach him a lesson.

14:57.520 --> 14:58.480
Come with me.

14:59.680 --> 15:01.880
- What's going on? You…
- I didn't touch her.

15:02.400 --> 15:03.280
Did you say you didn't?

15:03.360 --> 15:04.320
I saw it with my eyes.

15:04.400 --> 15:05.280
Xiaoduan is here.

15:05.360 --> 15:07.160
- How could you do that?
- I won't do it again.

15:07.240 --> 15:08.280
You're her big brother!

15:08.360 --> 15:09.560
Never again!

15:09.640 --> 15:10.760
Good, you know you're wrong.

15:19.640 --> 15:20.960
Can you get me a tissue?

15:39.160 --> 15:40.120
Do you and your brother

15:40.680 --> 15:41.960
do this often?

15:42.040 --> 15:43.240
It's nothing. Don't worry.

15:43.320 --> 15:44.880
Mom doesn't actually scold him.

15:45.360 --> 15:46.760
We've done this since we were kids.

15:47.360 --> 15:50.240
Didn't you ask Sang Yan for help just now?

15:50.320 --> 15:51.520
Why did you frame him then?

15:58.400 --> 15:59.440
Wait, little girl.

15:59.520 --> 16:00.840
Hold back your tears.

16:02.800 --> 16:03.680
What about this?

16:03.760 --> 16:05.320
I'll talk to Sang Yan

16:05.400 --> 16:06.440
and ask him to help you.

16:06.520 --> 16:07.600
What do you need?

16:07.680 --> 16:09.680
It won't work. He won't help me now.

16:09.760 --> 16:12.560
No, Sang Yan isn't that petty.

16:17.680 --> 16:19.520
Jiaxu, do you have time tomorrow?

16:22.640 --> 16:23.520
Tomorrow?

16:23.600 --> 16:24.960
Yes, tomorrow.

16:29.680 --> 16:30.720
What if I say

16:31.760 --> 16:32.920
I'm not free?

16:33.000 --> 16:33.880
No, you can't.

16:33.960 --> 16:34.880
You must be available.

16:34.960 --> 16:36.040
Why?

16:37.880 --> 16:39.360
If you hadn't told Sang Yan

16:40.040 --> 16:41.920
about the plastic surgery thing,

16:43.800 --> 16:45.160
I wouldn't have fought with him

16:46.440 --> 16:47.880
and he would have helped me.

16:53.120 --> 16:54.320
You might have a point.

16:55.880 --> 16:57.160
So tell me.

16:57.240 --> 16:58.560
What do you need me to do?

16:59.800 --> 17:00.960
Can you please

17:02.320 --> 17:03.960
pretend to be my brother?

17:04.800 --> 17:05.640
My real brother.

17:06.280 --> 17:07.160
And then,

17:08.040 --> 17:09.480
meet with my teacher.

17:12.040 --> 17:13.079
Are you in trouble at school?

17:15.960 --> 17:16.960
What have you done?

17:18.599 --> 17:19.680
Can I not tell?

17:19.760 --> 17:20.640
Sure.

17:21.520 --> 17:22.480
Then

17:23.040 --> 17:23.880
I'm busy tomorrow.

17:31.000 --> 17:32.480
I wasn't paying attention in class.

17:35.520 --> 17:37.240
I got called to answer a question.

17:38.360 --> 17:39.200
I answered correctly,

17:41.320 --> 17:43.120
but he wanted to meet with my parents.

17:47.040 --> 17:48.160
Do you expect me to buy that?

17:48.720 --> 17:49.800
I'm telling the truth.

17:51.240 --> 17:52.400
If you don't believe me,

17:52.480 --> 17:54.000
you'll find out tomorrow when you go.

17:54.520 --> 17:56.200
Even if I lie to you now,

17:56.280 --> 17:58.000
the teacher will tell you tomorrow.

17:59.280 --> 18:00.200
True.

18:01.360 --> 18:02.280
Little demon.

18:02.360 --> 18:03.560
Get out.

18:04.120 --> 18:05.200
Can't I stay here?

18:05.280 --> 18:06.520
I have to get changed.

18:07.440 --> 18:08.680
Weren't you doing it outside?

18:08.760 --> 18:10.320
I want to do it here now.

18:12.280 --> 18:13.840
If so, he should leave the room too.

18:14.680 --> 18:16.760
I don't think he wants to watch either.

18:18.400 --> 18:19.680
You two, get out.

18:23.680 --> 18:24.960
I'm going to undress.

18:29.120 --> 18:30.440
It took you long enough.

18:37.800 --> 18:38.960
Close the door.

18:54.720 --> 18:56.600
Jiaxu, are you coming or not tomorrow?

18:56.680 --> 18:57.920
I've told you everything.

18:58.640 --> 19:00.160
Why don't you ask Sang Yan?

19:00.240 --> 19:01.360
No way!

19:02.200 --> 19:03.600
I framed him just now.

19:04.280 --> 19:05.360
If I were to tell him…

19:05.920 --> 19:07.560
Sang Yan isn't like that.

19:07.640 --> 19:09.640
What are you mumbling about, little demon?

19:14.280 --> 19:16.040
A light bulb burned out.

19:22.520 --> 19:24.120
Mrs. Sang, I'm leaving.

19:24.840 --> 19:26.440
Leaving? Are you not staying for dinner?

19:26.520 --> 19:27.880
I've prepared many dishes.

19:27.960 --> 19:29.480
I have a part-time job later.

19:29.560 --> 19:30.440
Enjoy your meal.

19:30.520 --> 19:31.520
All right.

19:31.600 --> 19:32.800
What about you, Sang Yan?

19:33.440 --> 19:34.680
I'm not eating since he's not.

19:35.240 --> 19:36.920
Fine. Take this trash out for me.

19:37.000 --> 19:38.920
Take the boxes out first.

19:40.360 --> 19:41.240
Hurry up.

19:41.320 --> 19:42.400
I'll do it, Mrs. Sang.

19:42.480 --> 19:43.960
No, of course not. I…

19:44.040 --> 19:45.200
It's no big deal.

19:45.280 --> 19:46.280
I'm leaving.

19:46.360 --> 19:47.440
All right, thank you.

19:47.520 --> 19:48.720
Come for dinner next time.

19:48.800 --> 19:49.960
- Sure, Mrs. Sang.
- Good.

19:50.680 --> 19:52.360
- Bye, Mrs. Sang.
- Where are the boxes, Mom?

19:52.440 --> 19:53.720
They're right there.

19:55.520 --> 19:56.360
Bye, little girl.

19:56.920 --> 19:58.200
See you next time.

19:58.840 --> 20:00.080
Bye?

20:00.640 --> 20:02.320
Jiaxu, are you leaving so soon?

20:02.400 --> 20:03.560
It's getting late.

20:03.640 --> 20:05.120
Why don't you stay for dinner?

20:05.200 --> 20:06.080
Maybe next time.

20:06.160 --> 20:07.800
When is the next time?

20:09.560 --> 20:10.440
Duan Jiaxu.

20:10.520 --> 20:12.640
Don't waste your breath
with an elementary student.

20:12.720 --> 20:14.040
You're an elementary student.

20:14.120 --> 20:15.040
I'm in eighth grade.

20:15.720 --> 20:17.640
Gosh, you're an eighth-grader. Impressive.

20:17.720 --> 20:18.720
Are you in eighth grade?

20:19.200 --> 20:20.160
So,

20:20.960 --> 20:22.080
you're 14?

20:24.320 --> 20:26.200
Are you trying to say that I'm too short

20:26.280 --> 20:27.360
to be in eighth grade?

20:27.440 --> 20:29.520
Rightfully so. That's what he meant.

20:29.600 --> 20:30.880
No, that's not what I meant.

20:30.960 --> 20:32.200
Don't get me wrong.

20:33.600 --> 20:34.720
I won't argue with you.

20:34.800 --> 20:36.160
Anyway, I'll grow taller.

20:36.240 --> 20:38.040
No worries at all. You won't grow more.

20:38.120 --> 20:39.000
But it's good for you.

20:39.080 --> 20:40.840
At 30, people will think that you're 18.

20:42.320 --> 20:43.840
So is it because you're tall

20:43.920 --> 20:45.280
that people assume you're my dad?

20:52.080 --> 20:52.960
Bye.

20:53.520 --> 20:54.480
You're 14.

20:54.560 --> 20:55.600
What school do you go to?

20:56.160 --> 20:57.160
Xuri Middle-High School.

20:58.000 --> 20:59.160
Grade 8, Class 1.

21:00.800 --> 21:01.640
And your name?

21:02.640 --> 21:03.640
I'm Sang Zhi.

21:04.440 --> 21:05.520
Sang Zhi?

21:05.600 --> 21:07.040
Yes, "Zhi" as in innocence.

21:08.120 --> 21:09.120
Duan Jiaxu.

21:09.200 --> 21:10.880
- Let's go.
- I'm coming.

21:12.560 --> 21:13.560
So Sang Zhi,

21:14.520 --> 21:16.440
you know when we'll meet next time, right?

21:19.000 --> 21:19.880
Bye.

21:21.840 --> 21:23.560
Close the gate when you leave.

21:35.360 --> 21:36.320
<i>Next time?</i>

21:37.600 --> 21:38.480
<i>Hold on.</i>

21:39.080 --> 21:40.320
<i>When will that be?</i>

21:41.040 --> 21:42.120
<i>Tomorrow?</i>

21:43.280 --> 21:45.040
<i>So is he coming tomorrow or not?</i>

21:46.040 --> 21:47.800
<i>Why didn't he give me an exact answer?</i>

21:51.640 --> 21:53.240
CHAPTER ONE, WAITING

21:53.320 --> 21:55.000
A SECRET KEPT

22:25.040 --> 22:25.880
Mom.

22:26.480 --> 22:28.440
Good morning.

22:29.120 --> 22:30.480
Good morning.

22:32.960 --> 22:33.960
Good morning.

22:34.040 --> 22:35.320
Good morning, Sang Zhi!

22:35.800 --> 22:38.600
Good morning.

22:38.680 --> 22:39.840
Little demon.

22:39.920 --> 22:41.840
- Can't you see me?
- What's for breakfast?

22:41.920 --> 22:42.920
Hey!

22:43.520 --> 22:44.640
Little demon!

22:44.720 --> 22:45.600
Hi!

22:49.240 --> 22:50.760
Sang Yan, you're back.

22:52.160 --> 22:53.160
Yes, this is my home.

22:53.240 --> 22:54.440
Why can't I come back?

22:54.520 --> 22:56.600
So you know this is your home?

22:56.680 --> 22:58.120
When was the last time you were back?

22:58.200 --> 23:00.560
You can ask Dad and Mom
if they still recognize you.

23:02.520 --> 23:03.720
I haven't seen you for a month

23:03.800 --> 23:05.520
and you're giving me this attitude?

23:06.520 --> 23:08.520
What attitude do you expect from me then?

23:13.240 --> 23:14.760
<i>Welcome.</i>

23:14.840 --> 23:16.360
<i>A warm welcome to you.</i>

23:16.440 --> 23:17.840
<i>Welcome home, Sang Yan.</i>

23:17.920 --> 23:19.040
<i>Are you happy? Is this okay?</i>

23:19.120 --> 23:20.680
- I'm happy.
<i>- Let me give you a big hand.</i>

23:20.760 --> 23:22.040
- Well, stop it.
- Enough.

23:22.120 --> 23:23.680
- That's enough.
- The egg crepe is ready.

23:23.760 --> 23:24.920
- That's too much.
- Sit down.

23:26.280 --> 23:27.880
Hurry and try the egg crepe with tuna

23:27.960 --> 23:29.120
that your dad made for you.

23:36.640 --> 23:37.560
Nice.

23:40.440 --> 23:42.320
"My name is Sang Zhi
and this is how I talk."

23:42.800 --> 23:44.120
Stop making fun of her.

23:44.200 --> 23:45.760
- Come on.
- Eat up.

23:45.840 --> 23:46.720
Thank you, Dad.

23:46.800 --> 23:48.120
Dad, I'm moving back

23:48.200 --> 23:49.680
to the main campus.

23:49.760 --> 23:51.440
So I might need to borrow your car.

23:51.520 --> 23:52.640
Do you have a lot of things?

23:52.720 --> 23:54.200
I can get you a moving company.

23:54.840 --> 23:56.880
No, this is better than the campus bus.

23:56.960 --> 23:58.480
I remember that the main campus

23:58.560 --> 24:00.280
is near Zhizhi's school.

24:01.480 --> 24:03.880
You can pick up Zhizhi from school
from now on.

24:03.960 --> 24:04.880
I'm in university now.

24:04.960 --> 24:06.160
I'm not babysitting her.

24:06.240 --> 24:07.640
I don't need him. I'm in 11th grade.

24:08.200 --> 24:09.200
That had best be the case.

24:09.760 --> 24:11.960
Dad, can I borrow your car this morning?

24:12.040 --> 24:14.080
I'm fetching my roommate's things too.

24:14.760 --> 24:17.200
Yes, as long as you don't bully Sang Zhi.

24:17.960 --> 24:19.200
Fine, I'll try to.

24:21.760 --> 24:22.760
Which roommate?

24:23.360 --> 24:24.240
Why do you ask?

24:33.920 --> 24:35.160
What do you want?

24:38.880 --> 24:40.960
Sang Yan, how about I help you move?

24:42.200 --> 24:43.600
Do you want to help me move?

24:49.720 --> 24:51.200
Did I mishear you?

24:51.280 --> 24:52.560
No, you didn't.

24:54.160 --> 24:55.160
You need to go to school.

24:55.960 --> 24:57.600
I can go after school.

24:58.480 --> 24:59.880
You won't be done that early anyway.

24:59.960 --> 25:01.000
May I?

25:01.080 --> 25:02.000
Zhizhi.

25:02.080 --> 25:04.400
Your art science subject tests
are in a few days.

25:04.480 --> 25:06.120
You have to study at school.

25:06.200 --> 25:07.440
I've already done the revision.

25:07.520 --> 25:08.760
I can take a few days off.

25:09.520 --> 25:11.120
Do your revision.

25:11.200 --> 25:13.720
Besides, I'm sure
I'll have finished moving

25:13.800 --> 25:15.080
by the time you come.

25:16.080 --> 25:17.760
Mom, Dad.

25:17.840 --> 25:19.880
Sang Yan hasn't been home in a long time.

25:20.440 --> 25:22.280
I've been missing him so much.

25:23.120 --> 25:24.360
I'm grown up now

25:24.440 --> 25:26.000
and I should do something for him.

25:26.080 --> 25:28.200
Sang Yan, look how sincere she is.

25:28.280 --> 25:29.280
Just let her help.

25:29.360 --> 25:31.480
- That's right.
- She won't affect your studies.

25:32.080 --> 25:32.960
Wait.

25:33.040 --> 25:35.160
How can she help? My things are heavy.

25:35.240 --> 25:36.400
She can't move them at all.

25:36.480 --> 25:38.080
I'll have to keep her from getting hurt.

25:38.160 --> 25:39.080
If she gets hurt,

25:39.160 --> 25:40.920
I'll be in big trouble when I come home.

25:41.000 --> 25:42.760
Just let her keep an eye on your things.

25:42.840 --> 25:43.840
Isn't that good?

25:46.520 --> 25:47.640
Fine, do what you like.

25:52.280 --> 25:54.600
I'll call you after school.

25:59.800 --> 26:00.680
Do you want this?

26:02.000 --> 26:02.880
I'm eating this.

26:22.800 --> 26:23.840
Hello.

26:24.400 --> 26:25.280
Hello.

26:27.400 --> 26:28.320
I'm here.

26:28.400 --> 26:30.360
You actually came?

26:30.960 --> 26:31.840
Where are you?

26:31.920 --> 26:33.200
<i>I'm too busy to come get you.</i>

26:33.280 --> 26:34.160
<i>Wait for me there.</i>

26:36.600 --> 26:38.440
Tell me where you are now.

26:38.520 --> 26:39.440
I'll come find you.

26:40.000 --> 26:41.000
Block 9, Room 525.

26:41.960 --> 26:42.960
Block 9.

26:44.520 --> 26:45.440
Got it.

26:51.680 --> 26:52.640
Silly Dog.

26:56.320 --> 26:57.520
<i>It's Dad's car.</i>

27:16.760 --> 27:18.400
ISAAC ASIMOV: THE END OF ETERNITY

27:18.480 --> 27:20.280
DUAN

27:20.360 --> 27:21.640
Busted, thief.

27:33.320 --> 27:34.480
Sang Zhi?

27:37.960 --> 27:38.960
It has been some years.

27:39.040 --> 27:40.240
I hardly recognized you.

27:44.440 --> 27:46.720
I'm here to help my brother move.

27:46.800 --> 27:48.240
I know. He told me.

27:49.280 --> 27:50.960
But why did you only steal my things?

27:52.760 --> 27:54.200
Is this yours?

27:56.480 --> 27:57.440
I…

27:57.920 --> 28:00.160
I didn't know it was yours.

28:00.240 --> 28:02.240
Had I known, I wouldn't have touched it.

28:03.640 --> 28:05.840
What do you mean by that?

28:07.920 --> 28:10.200
Kiddo, where is your conscience?

28:11.240 --> 28:13.320
I did you a great favor.
Don't you remember?

28:15.240 --> 28:16.160
No.

28:19.960 --> 28:22.400
If you like this plushie, take it.

28:22.960 --> 28:24.040
I was kidding.

28:27.120 --> 28:28.440
I'm already in 11th grade.

28:29.200 --> 28:30.880
I don't play with plushies anymore.

28:32.640 --> 28:33.920
I see.

28:34.000 --> 28:35.680
I'll throw it away then.

28:35.760 --> 28:37.520
I…

28:37.600 --> 28:39.880
I can play with it for a while.

28:46.400 --> 28:48.000
Come on. I'll take you upstairs.

28:49.280 --> 28:50.920
You can take your brother's shoes.

29:00.200 --> 29:01.120
Let's go.

29:09.800 --> 29:10.680
Jiaxu.

29:11.440 --> 29:12.760
Did you get this fox plushie

29:13.840 --> 29:15.280
from someone else?

29:16.480 --> 29:17.360
I think so.

29:17.840 --> 29:18.800
I can't remember.

29:25.480 --> 29:26.680
We have to walk up five floors.

29:26.760 --> 29:27.760
Can you do it?

29:29.360 --> 29:30.600
This way.

29:37.560 --> 29:38.440
Sang Yan.

29:40.840 --> 29:43.040
You said you were too busy to get me.

29:43.120 --> 29:43.960
You're not busy!

29:44.040 --> 29:45.760
You just didn't want to come to get me.

29:46.760 --> 29:48.880
I just finished up and sat down to rest.

29:48.960 --> 29:50.120
No, you didn't.

29:50.200 --> 29:51.480
You didn't move at all.

29:51.560 --> 29:53.120
You didn't tidy up just now.

29:53.200 --> 29:54.600
Mom asked you to fetch me.

29:59.880 --> 30:02.000
- Give that to me.
- Sang Yan.

30:02.680 --> 30:03.520
Is this your sister?

30:04.080 --> 30:05.200
Yes.

30:05.280 --> 30:06.160
Greet Qian Fei.

30:06.960 --> 30:09.200
Hello, Qian Fei. I'm Sang Zhi.

30:11.520 --> 30:12.400
Little girl,

30:12.480 --> 30:13.440
you're so adorable!

30:15.280 --> 30:16.120
Keep your distance.

30:16.200 --> 30:17.160
It's our first meeting.

30:17.240 --> 30:18.480
Why can't I go near her?

30:18.560 --> 30:19.600
Besides, I'm short-sighted.

30:19.680 --> 30:21.640
You'll scare her if you get too close.

30:22.880 --> 30:24.320
I'm sorry about that.

30:24.400 --> 30:25.840
Don't be.

30:25.920 --> 30:26.920
Come here, little girl.

30:28.520 --> 30:29.520
Sit over here.

30:34.040 --> 30:34.960
Sit over there.

30:41.080 --> 30:42.080
I'm not little.

30:46.360 --> 30:47.760
I said I'm not little.

30:49.600 --> 30:50.440
All right,

30:51.160 --> 30:52.440
girl.

30:59.520 --> 31:00.840
What do we have for dinner?

31:00.920 --> 31:02.680
We've finally moved here

31:02.760 --> 31:04.000
and your sister is here too.

31:04.080 --> 31:05.360
Let's not eat at the canteen.

31:06.080 --> 31:07.800
There's a good hot pot place in the mall.

31:07.880 --> 31:09.040
What do you say?

31:10.600 --> 31:11.440
Let's eat barbecue.

31:11.520 --> 31:13.200
There's a food street off campus.

31:13.280 --> 31:14.200
Let's try that out.

31:14.960 --> 31:15.960
Hot pot, please.

31:16.040 --> 31:17.600
Haven't you had enough barbecue?

31:19.080 --> 31:20.320
DIRECT ADMISSION RECOMMENDATION

31:20.400 --> 31:21.280
Little demon.

31:21.360 --> 31:22.640
Hey, little demon.

31:23.400 --> 31:24.920
Do you want a hot pot or barbecue?

31:25.800 --> 31:27.640
Jiaxu, let's have a hot pot tonight.

31:30.480 --> 31:31.680
You guys go.

31:31.760 --> 31:33.040
I have my part-time job later.

31:35.640 --> 31:36.640
Seriously, Jiaxu?

31:37.160 --> 31:38.360
Where are you going?

31:38.440 --> 31:40.000
Don't tell me you have a girlfriend.

31:40.080 --> 31:41.400
You can't be the only one dating.

31:41.480 --> 31:43.480
- Introduce a girl to me.
- Introduce one to me first.

31:43.560 --> 31:44.920
Don't cut in line. Me first.

31:45.000 --> 31:46.320
Any girl who isn't hot-tempered.

31:46.400 --> 31:47.440
Any girl will do

31:47.520 --> 31:48.640
as long as she likes me.

31:49.280 --> 31:50.160
Qian Fei.

31:50.800 --> 31:52.240
My brother told me

31:52.320 --> 31:53.960
all the girls in school pursued him.

32:04.600 --> 32:05.960
Well, little girl.

32:06.040 --> 32:07.040
I have never seen someone

32:07.120 --> 32:09.160
more thick-skinned than him!

32:09.240 --> 32:10.320
I suppose Sang Yan

32:10.400 --> 32:11.800
has been more handsome lately.

32:11.880 --> 32:12.960
Get away from me.

32:24.520 --> 32:25.440
You guys talk.

32:25.520 --> 32:26.440
I'm off.

32:33.120 --> 32:34.120
Girl.

32:35.120 --> 32:37.400
If you like it, take it with you.

32:40.320 --> 32:41.600
Bye.

32:44.160 --> 32:45.600
<i>He's leaving so soon.</i>

32:54.400 --> 32:55.880
Duan Jiaxu hasn't thrown that away.

32:55.960 --> 32:56.960
What's wrong with him?

32:59.720 --> 33:02.160
It's just a decoration on his bed.

33:02.240 --> 33:03.600
It's completely useless.

33:06.400 --> 33:07.360
By the way, Qian Fei.

33:09.080 --> 33:11.360
Does Jiaxu have a girlfriend?

33:11.440 --> 33:13.000
Did his girlfriend give him this?

33:15.960 --> 33:17.360
He doesn't have a girlfriend.

33:17.960 --> 33:19.960
He's busy every day

33:20.040 --> 33:21.480
and has no time for dating.

33:22.000 --> 33:23.920
I think it was a prize from some event.

33:24.480 --> 33:25.600
It was from last semester.

33:27.480 --> 33:29.200
If you don't like it, just leave it there.

33:29.280 --> 33:30.800
That dog must have made a fool of you.

33:32.760 --> 33:33.640
Dog?

33:33.720 --> 33:35.120
Don't you know?

33:35.200 --> 33:36.320
He and your brother are known

33:36.400 --> 33:37.480
as the Twin Dogs of Nanwu.

33:39.080 --> 33:40.720
I thought Sang Yan was the only dog.

33:45.280 --> 33:46.240
Enough of that.

33:46.320 --> 33:47.800
Do you want a hot pot or barbecue?

33:48.720 --> 33:49.600
Neither.

33:50.640 --> 33:51.480
What do you want?

33:51.560 --> 33:52.720
I'll drive you home after.

33:53.280 --> 33:54.760
No need. I want to go home now.

33:54.840 --> 33:55.720
I'm not eating.

33:56.360 --> 33:58.040
I can drive you home.

33:58.520 --> 34:00.040
I'll take the bus.

34:01.440 --> 34:02.600
Really?

34:03.640 --> 34:04.960
Fine, it's almost time. Let's go.

34:06.800 --> 34:07.920
I'm leaving.

34:08.000 --> 34:09.400
- Bye!
- Bye. See you next time.

34:17.520 --> 34:19.440
"Asimov.

34:19.520 --> 34:21.120
<i>The End of Eternity</i>.

34:24.360 --> 34:26.159
But it resolves itself

34:26.239 --> 34:27.719
into an identity.

34:29.080 --> 34:31.239
There is a loop of small dimensions

34:31.320 --> 34:33.880
with no tributaries

34:35.199 --> 34:37.199
on either side."

34:40.040 --> 34:41.040
Can you understand this?

34:52.800 --> 34:54.960
Maybe this is the distance between us.

34:57.560 --> 34:59.480
I can't understand the book he is reading.

35:01.600 --> 35:02.720
I only know the characters.

35:05.080 --> 35:07.360
Sang Yan, how is your thesis coming along?

35:08.520 --> 35:09.600
I need more references.

35:09.680 --> 35:11.600
- I'll go to the library tomorrow.
- You're focused.

35:11.680 --> 35:13.040
I haven't finished my thesis yet.

35:13.120 --> 35:14.480
I haven't either.

35:17.440 --> 35:18.480
Why are you back?

35:18.560 --> 35:19.760
I brought some food for you.

35:19.840 --> 35:21.320
Help yourselves.

35:21.400 --> 35:22.240
- Okay.
- Sure.

35:23.720 --> 35:24.960
It's all your fault.

35:25.040 --> 35:26.520
You're always bringing food from work.

35:26.600 --> 35:28.160
That's why I'm so chubby. I blame you.

35:29.400 --> 35:30.520
Jiaxu.

35:30.600 --> 35:31.760
My sister called me just now

35:31.840 --> 35:33.280
and said you left something with her.

35:33.880 --> 35:35.080
Did I leave something with her?

35:35.160 --> 35:36.080
Hold on.

35:36.920 --> 35:37.840
I'll call her.

35:39.400 --> 35:43.680
SILLY DOG

35:46.720 --> 35:47.880
<i>Did you find it?</i>

35:47.960 --> 35:48.800
Kiddo.

35:48.880 --> 35:50.320
<i>What did I leave behind with you?</i>

35:56.680 --> 35:58.840
No, you didn't leave something with me.

35:58.920 --> 36:00.800
I left something at your place.

36:02.160 --> 36:03.000
<i>What is it?</i>

36:05.560 --> 36:06.760
An exercise book.

36:08.800 --> 36:09.640
I'll ask Sang Yan

36:09.720 --> 36:11.120
to bring it to you tomorrow morning.

36:12.640 --> 36:14.160
But I haven't done my homework yet.

36:17.400 --> 36:18.920
Are you asking me to do it for you?

36:20.720 --> 36:21.600
No.

36:23.160 --> 36:25.080
It's because it's an essay.

36:26.600 --> 36:28.080
I might not have time to finish it.

36:28.880 --> 36:30.640
Why don't you ask Sang Yan
to do it for you?

36:32.280 --> 36:34.080
He would break my legs.

36:46.200 --> 36:47.040
Sang Zhi.

36:47.760 --> 36:48.680
This homework

36:48.760 --> 36:50.440
is a task assigned by your teacher.

36:51.400 --> 36:53.400
You can be honest with the teacher,

36:53.480 --> 36:54.360
apologize,

36:54.440 --> 36:55.960
and say you will complete it afterward.

36:56.040 --> 36:57.680
You shouldn't ask someone
to do it for you.

37:06.280 --> 37:07.960
What time do you usually arrive at school?

37:08.840 --> 37:10.000
7:40 a.m.

37:10.520 --> 37:11.560
<i>7:40 a.m.</i>

37:12.080 --> 37:13.400
<i>So you wake up at 7:00 a.m.</i>

37:13.480 --> 37:16.520
<i>Can you wake up at 6:00 a.m. tomorrow?</i>

37:17.000 --> 37:17.960
Why?

37:19.000 --> 37:20.200
Tomorrow,

37:20.280 --> 37:23.000
I'll wait for you at the bus stop
at 6:40 a.m.

37:23.080 --> 37:24.320
<i>I'll help you write the essay.</i>

37:24.400 --> 37:25.320
<i>Is that okay?</i>

37:30.960 --> 37:32.720
If so, you should plan out

37:32.800 --> 37:34.200
what you will write.

37:34.280 --> 37:36.320
After that, wash up and go to bed.

37:37.800 --> 37:38.680
All right.

37:40.480 --> 37:41.560
<i>6:00 a.m.</i>

37:41.640 --> 37:43.040
<i>Remember to set the alarm.</i>

37:43.120 --> 37:44.360
<i>I'll call you then.</i>

37:46.400 --> 37:47.600
Go to sleep now.

37:47.680 --> 37:48.640
<i>Good night.</i>

37:57.000 --> 37:58.560
CALL LOG

37:58.640 --> 38:01.440
LITTLE DEMON

38:12.560 --> 38:13.800
- Your phone.
- What is it?

38:15.240 --> 38:16.200
What did you forget?

38:17.200 --> 38:18.040
It's trivial.

38:21.400 --> 38:22.920
What time are you going to the library?

38:23.000 --> 38:24.040
First thing in the morning.

38:24.120 --> 38:25.160
As early as possible.

38:25.240 --> 38:26.160
Why so early?

